# APP_ENV: 운영은 production (lifespan이 ML 모델 로드 실패 시 startup 차단).
# 미설정 또는 비-production 값이면 Stub Simulator로 fallback.
APP_ENV=local
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/noxo
# Production ML snapshot mode requires explicit DB column mapping JSON.
# Include every RAW_FEATURES + TARGETS tag from digital_twin.preprocess.
# SENSOR_COLUMN_MAPPING='{"<igcc_tag>":"<sensor_data_column>"}'
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379/0
PORT=8000
